OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start this morning
OL,6,Fwith spells of hazy sunshine. Cloud
OL,7,Fmay tend to thicken into this
OL,8,Fafternoon with one or two showers
OL,9,Fpossible, especially towards Cumbria
OL,10,Fand Lancashire. Feeling warm in any
OL,11,Fsunshine and light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe odd shower may continue
OL,14,Finto this evening, before turning dry
OL,15,Fovernight with a mix of cloud and
OL,16,Fclear spells. The odd spot of grass
OL,17,Ffrost possible in the countryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
