OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAnother bright day with spells
OL,6,Fof sunshine, best of which will be
OL,7,Ftowards the west. The odd shower
OL,8,Fpossible in the east come the
OL,9,Fafternoon, but many areas staying dry.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FStaying dry and settled during the
OL,13,Ffinal days of April with spells of
OL,14,Fsunshine. Feeling warm in the
OL,15,Fsunshine, but nights still on the
OL,16,Fchilly side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
